{"tid":835260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無係出到街先知今日係中秋節","createTime":"2018-09-24T17:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T04:34:03.000Z","uid":45728,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"82cd3d866f1043ad665935ead8f3c174522deea6","tid":835260,"uid":45728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"小弟平時做夜班工作<br />\n今日早收工 10點已經返到家 <br />\n係屋企訓醒經已下午6點<br />\n想落街食個飯 行行下發覺好多鋪頭都無開門 <br />\n心諗咩野日子唔撚洗做咁 原來今日已經中秋節<br />\n最後自己一個去左大家樂食焗豬飯<br />\n我係到望下隔離左右 原來大家樂都好多自己一條友黎食飯既人 我諗坐得係到既 都係工作到唔知時候 <br />\n默默地為家人同自己努力緊既人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/015453_dda5a596a3389548266aec5f939228dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F015453_dda5a596a3389548266aec5f939228dd.png&h=2f60343a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c1518df900055a605c4628cb435c67b35e28f4e","tid":835260,"uid":211727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T18:07:39.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒啊巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做嘢忙起上嚟連聖誕節嚟到都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e09a543161dacc3bc37c3bb1c668d3a25c21de9","tid":835260,"uid":211727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辛苦晒啊巴<span style=\"color: red;\">打</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做嘢忙起上嚟連聖誕節嚟到都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9829afe8043268bee709a3e08d0a06fe741a8147","tid":835260,"uid":29702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4765d36b19c4dfa4b2591a89527c4c3110942878","tid":835260,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T18:10:03.000Z","msg":"搞錯呀 唔食洋蔥"},{"pid":"b2a775739062bc9b15f12145bf123caac5b3640e","tid":835260,"uid":45728,"like":0